<br>
Iraq, on the other hand, is extremely wealthy in terms of natural resources.  The United States has the ability to bankroll military action today, set a puppet government in place, and then negotiate contracts with that government to ensure low-cost oil for many decades to come.<br>
<br>
It is Economic Conquest with Iraq being held under the imperial control of the United States through contracts.<br>
<br>
Iraq will be an Endentured Servant to the United States until it is no longer considered a profitible venture.<br>
